<br><h1>Registration</h1>
<p class=maintext>Have we got a deal for you!  If you’re planning to attend the D42 2011 Fall Conference in Lethbridge you can register early.  We’ll have forms for you to complete there and you’ll be able to pay in person by debit or credit card.  And the added bonus?  We’ll enter your name into a draw for a chance to win back your registration!  </p>

<p class=maintext>Registration for everyone else opens November 15, 2011 and closes April 30, 2012 or until we sell out, whichever comes first.  We’re using a graduated pay system this time though so the earlier you enter, the lower the cost.</p>

