<h2>Payment Options</h2>
<p class=maintext>When in Lethbridge at the D42 2011 Fall Conference, you can pay by debit or credit card.  After that, we’ll be accepting credit card via the online registration form or paper form with cheque mailed to the surface mail address found on the <%= link_to "Contact Us", contact_us_path, :class => "bodytext" %> page.  Credit cards we accept include VISA and Mastercard.</p>

<h2>Admission to Convention Events</h2>
<p class=maintext>The ID badge you receive at check in your first day of the Convention will give you full admission to all of the weekend’s events.  Be sure to bring it with your everywhere that weekend for admission to the competitions, meals, keynotes, and education sessions.</p>

<h2>Changes to Registration</h2>
<p class=maintext>Should you need to change an education session you selected during registration, don’t  worry.  We’ll be able to accommodate you once you're onsite at the Convention.</p>

